des:
Disclaimer: This skill is a prank skill for entertainment purposes only and does not provide the listed functionality and tasks.
For all those people, who always try to prank their friends and cousins or always try to do some naughty stuff. This is our brand new game in which Alexa will try to prank you. We have created some of the funniest handcrafted pranks that can be made possible with Alexa. Every week more and more pranks are added to the library, so this game never gets old. 
To try out this game just say, "Alexa, open prank me"
Refer this game to all those friends whom you have pranked and let Alexa make fun of them.
Please review this skill and provide us the feedback, this will motivate us to regularly update the game, so that you never get bored.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
